# ✍️ AI Quote Generator

An LSTM-based text generation app that predicts and continues quotes word-by-word, built with Keras and deployed using Streamlit.

## Overview

This project trains an LSTM language model on a quotes dataset to predict the next word given a starting phrase (seed text), then repeatedly generates words to form a continuation.

## Tech Stack

- Python, TensorFlow/Keras (LSTM)
- Streamlit (deployment)

## Pipeline

1. Text cleaning (lowercase, punctuation removal)
2. Tokenization (Keras Tokenizer, vocab_size=10000)
3. Sequence generation (prefix → next-word pairs)
4. Padding (pre-padding to max_len)
5. One-hot encoding of target words
6. Model: Embedding → LSTM(128) → Dense(softmax)
7. Trained with categorical_crossentropy, Adam optimizer

## Run Locally

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run app.py
```

